      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MANAGER (1) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 2.5 lengths win at this track in a handy 25.11. Has the coveted inside box and likes the trip. Winner at his latest appearance in the quickest time on the card. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. FEAR THE BEER (7) had been in sparkling form with a two start winning streak coming to an end last time finishing third (25.95) at Warrnambool. Solid record here winning three races. Best form too dangerous to ignore. Have to include. MOYARRA KONGK (8) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (25.40) last time out at Ballarat. Strike rate this course and distance strong having won two of three tries. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Overdue and gets his chance. PHOENIX TAN (2) is worth some thought after placing last start.",
